text: KYBU (96.9 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Covelo, California. The station is owned by Friends of the Round Valley Public Library, and airs a variety format. The station was assigned the call sign KQZT by the Federal Communications Commission on May 23, 2007. The station changed its call sign to KYBU on December 7, 2011. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * YBU Category:Radio stations established in 2011 Category:2011 establishments in California Category:Variety radio stations in the United States Category:Community radio stations in the United States Category:Mendocino County, California
